bits.comment:
Magic number, only when this field is 0x8800, the efuse programming command can be handle.
Set the magic number right will lock the power switch and PGM enable.
So if SW want to program efuse memory, except open clocks and power, 2 other conditions must be met :
(1) SEC_EFUSE_MAGIC_NUMBER =0x8800
(2) PG_EN=1;
(3) Switch the power right;

SEC/NON-SEC address configure. 
   1: indicates SEC can access EFUSE_CFG0;
   0: indicates NON-SEC can access EFUSE_CFG0;
